Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.72,0:24:20.04,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}青春是冒险之旅  朝着究极之梦进发
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.04,0:24:25.63,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}争取所爱像野外求生  随随便便可不行  给我认真点
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.12,0:24:25.63,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}（一  二  三  四  五  六）
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.71,0:24:31.02,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}光靠可爱可不行  隐藏技能也得好好修炼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.02,0:24:36.54,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}倒立柔软运动样样行  无限喷嚏哈啾  啦啦啦啦No.1
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.54,0:24:41.08,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}走这走那走到脚软  补充活力快张嘴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.08,0:24:47.15,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}实现梦想靠胡来  坚强美丽地盛开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.20,0:24:51.11,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}依靠唯一的穹苍  好  现在开始
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.72,0:24:58.17,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}逆境才是好机会  不管风吹雨打
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.32,0:25:03.05,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}快来吧  快来  展开身体迎接风雨
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.41,0:25:08.95,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}超越一切困难  好想见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.03,0:25:13.92,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想见你  想见你  放马过来吧
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------PREV-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.80,0:00:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  都说不要了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.51,0:00:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咯吱咯吱  咯吱咯吱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.96,0:00:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快停手  姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.73,0:00:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.59,0:00:21.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.26,0:00:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.07,0:00:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不…来得正好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.78,0:00:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是小一的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.34,0:00:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把它落在游泳池边了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.48,0:00:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  谢谢你哦  我去交给她
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.14,0:00:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.59,0:00:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.87,0:00:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目你…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.33,0:00:41.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是渚同学的…姐姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你听见了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.17,0:00:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.72,0:00:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TITLE-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.00,0:02:27.00,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(329,300)\blur10}暗影显现
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------TEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,异母姐妹？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.61,0:02:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们在同一天出生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.22,0:02:36.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲也是同一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不为人所知的秘密姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.13,0:02:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难怪了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.49,0:02:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别多管闲事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.14,0:02:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请不要再追问了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:47.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:48.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过刚刚的话要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.98,0:02:57.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但小一承受着巨大的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.83,0:02:59.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对绝对要保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.38,0:03:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:03.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不会对任何人说起的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.72,0:03:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.57,0:03:09.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  不知不觉就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.10,0:03:14.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,渚同学大概也是这种感受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要上厕所？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真羡慕天女目呢  总感觉你很自由
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.08,0:03:32.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？我很自由吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说  总觉得你这样很棒就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.43,0:03:40.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.54,0:03:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲刺！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.07,0:03:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.86,0:03:58.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.32,0:04:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再见咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迟到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.49,0:04:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚饭是要吃速成咖喱了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.29,0:04:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:18.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小瑛她很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开朗  又平易近人  真羡慕她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么她能那么坚强呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.09,0:04:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穹  饭做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.06,0:04:43.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是夏祭的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.00,0:04:52.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是你迷路的时候吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.26,0:04:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个是？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:57.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:04:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是悠送给我的礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.82,0:05:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是母亲的遗物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.66,0:05:18.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  已经要出门了？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.93,0:05:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那啥  今天轮到我值日
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  悠  早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.06,0:05:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你总是来得好早呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.65,0:05:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  因为要换花儿呀
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.89,0:06:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是悠你来得好早呀  怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.11,0:06:12.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了对了  我有些事想单独和天女目谈谈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们…以前见过面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.17,0:06:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠你果然还记得我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.72,0:06:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起…又来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:47.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我真的超开心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.79,0:06:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  能想起来真的好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.58,0:06:53.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等着
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.54,0:07:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏祭的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得我们一起去捉知了了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.10,0:07:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说  要抓一只珍奇的知了送给我  然后爬上了树
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.92,0:07:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼疼疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.86,0:07:57.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀  连这都被你想起来了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:07:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.66,0:08:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.94,0:08:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  这都是多早的事情了  别介意别介意了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:09.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过  除此以外再没有母亲别的遗物了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说我连母亲的记忆都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.46,0:08:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找不到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.13,0:08:27.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.07,0:08:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧  别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.35,0:08:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.74,0:08:58.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.85,0:09:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找吧  去找你母亲的挂坠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.88,0:09:01.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.75,0:09:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这个星期天…不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:05.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以倒是可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:07.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就说定了  明天见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.66,0:09:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这身打扮是要去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.75,0:09:33.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这事关个人隐私所以我不能说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.93,0:09:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谁一起？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.23,0:09:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  嗯  和亮平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是星期天的说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.35,0:09:43.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.43,0:09:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:09:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你浑身充满干劲呢  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.77,0:09:59.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.39,0:10:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是天女目  你这身打扮没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.40,0:10:05.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  没问题哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.31,0:10:06.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好  出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.03,0:10:08.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.45,0:10:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  等等  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.10,0:10:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我记得在这前面的杉树
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.17,0:10:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对面  就是我们捉知了的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.74,0:10:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.75,0:10:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果弄丢了  就是丢在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.32,0:10:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  我没事先告诉你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.49,0:10:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候爬的树
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.57,0:10:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被三年前的水土流失给冲走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经没有了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.13,0:10:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.54,0:10:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目你在那儿等着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.70,0:10:59.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这怎么可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太勉强了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.29,0:11:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.77,0:11:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.04,0:11:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经够了  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,换个地方看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.00,0:11:49.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.52,0:11:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你要为我做到这种地步
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:11:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般来说不用做到这种地步的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.68,0:11:59.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你弄丢挂坠的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.60,0:12:07.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然马上露出笑脸对我说  不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.94,0:12:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但当你一个人的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.25,0:12:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你的表情变得很忧伤
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.30,0:12:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\q2}而最近的那个早晨  我在教室又看到你和那时一样忧伤的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.38,0:12:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你其实一直都藏着忧伤吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没这回事…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:33.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我想让天女目能够一直露出笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.77,0:12:34.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.17,0:12:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我绝不会放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.91,0:12:51.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不会放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.06,0:13:02.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  悠  你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.17,0:13:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  天女目呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.32,0:13:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.43,0:13:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了  我会尽快洗好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.82,0:13:18.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.83,0:13:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服也没那么快烘干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把浴巾放这了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:24.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.95,0:13:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:45.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.23,0:13:51.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久没听见了  有人进来的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.62,0:13:55.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去都是爷爷先泡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.88,0:13:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再「呀呵」一下走进来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.43,0:14:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得很让人怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.35,0:14:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:05.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先洗吧  我等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.39,0:14:08.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.80,0:14:36.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来咯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.95,0:14:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.07,0:14:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.37,0:14:42.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:50.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到脸的话会难为情的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过去经常像这样坐在爷爷的膝盖上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.28,0:14:56.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.74,0:14:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.49,0:15:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像碰到很硬的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.74,0:15:03.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.67,0:15:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.72,0:15:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么有兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.06,0:15:10.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你问什么  就像这样子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.92,0:15:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天女目
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是不是在做坏事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.98,0:15:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是悠的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡晕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:43.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那肯定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.94,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉依姬大人  我做了遭报应的事真是对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.28,0:15:58.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的母亲…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.85,0:16:01.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去世了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.39,0:16:02.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.02,0:16:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是说不定还在世
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.50,0:16:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.18,0:16:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.47,0:16:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一带的孩子全都由我奶奶负责过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.91,0:16:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许会留下什么记录
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:24.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有这个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.88,0:16:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过你的母亲可能也很想见你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:46.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人太多  头都要晕了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.08,0:17:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找个地方休息一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.16,0:17:17.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.70,0:17:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会有蚊子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.11,0:17:22.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.70,0:17:24.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.84,0:17:30.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你等下不是要上台跳舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:36.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上场的时候就会认真加油的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.72,0:17:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.21,0:18:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.07,0:18:18.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母亲大人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.16,0:18:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初佳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.32,0:18:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:24.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,供奉用的各种物品都准备好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.58,0:18:26.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  准备齐全
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.70,0:18:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以来都对不起了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.18,0:18:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去准备跳舞了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉依姬是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.90,0:19:02.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是供奉在这里的神灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这点我还是懂的  我不是问这个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉依姬是一位喜欢过几名人类的神灵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是人们却无法接受叉依姬的神圣与庄严
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果都离她而去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉依姬把这份悲伤藏在笑容背后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:25.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最终决定一直默默地为人类的幸福祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.76,0:19:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌这样的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.30,0:20:14.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.25,0:20:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上回来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.96,0:20:37.97,incn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs30}待续
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//--------------------M---------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.89,0:22:11.64,title3,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)}想屡战屡胜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.13,0:22:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啦  初佳
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为只有立直…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.37,0:22:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实还有三宝牌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:21.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  算上里宝一共七宝牌！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.69,0:22:24.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初佳小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.92,0:22:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,八寻姐姐好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.02,0:22:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧  初佳小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.72,0:22:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会来拯救我吗  悠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.00,0:22:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话啊初佳  那是当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.74,0:22:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,悠
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.49,0:22:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是犯花痴的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:46.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错  我通过这场对局来占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能超过零分  那他对我也有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.11,0:22:52.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还能胜出的话  就能和他顺利交往
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.92,0:22:55.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能在这里胡出起死回生的役满…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.84,0:23:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该打哪张好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.04,0:23:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点吧  瑛  怎么想都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.64,0:23:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.55,0:23:13.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恋人确定？不
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.02,0:23:17.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是老公确定？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.84,0:23:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这种玩法吗  老公
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.72,0:23:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为游戏里没有这个场景
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.38,0:23:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是执着的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.39,0:23:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  那里  不能挤…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.29,0:23:46.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  自摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.66,0:23:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初佳小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.19,0:23:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的总结
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:56.87,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}国破山河在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:56.87,pos,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.20,0:23:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待续
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,//------------------NEXT-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.46,0:25:33.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的笑容背后所封闭的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.91,0:25:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算能被明亮地照耀
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.21,0:25:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定会伤害到他人
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.33,0:25:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  悠  这样子就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.39,0:25:44.94,next,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(320,280)}瑛不言弃


